  "texts": [
    "It uses word and topic embeddings to interpret latent topics following Dieng et al (2020).",
    "The topic embeddings at slice t depend on topic embeddings at slice t -1.",
    "Besides, it uses a LSTM to learn temporal priors of doc-topic distributions.",
    "Rahimi et al (2023) discover topic evolution by clustering documents but cannot infer doc-topic distributions as required.",
    "Zhang and Lauw (2022) focus on the dynamic topics of temporal document networks and incorporate the linking information between documents."
